-- Free Write Open Studio - Write Pittsburgh
Mondays, 7:30-9 p.m.
Get Tickets
Literary
Writing can be a lonely endeavor. That's why a writing community is so important. Join us for our low-key online open studio hours every Monday night from 7:30 to 9:00 p.m. ET. Drop in for as long as you like. We’ll check in every half hour or so to let you brag about your accomplishments (or cry on a sympathetic shoulder if that’s what you need). Register at bit.ly/WPghStudio for the Zoom link.This program is for adult writers, ages 18+.


